Everything is looking a little squashed up against the side of the boxes. It would be nice if there were
a little spacing around the edges. To achieve this we add a margin and some left and right padding to the
body and section elements, and small images. Add these rules in one line at a time and see the effects.

Daniel also plays clarinet and is learning the alto saxophone.
